title: Benghazi panel's new facts focus on 'four dead Americans,' not Clinton 2016 bid
text: Hillary Clinton’s upcoming testimony before Congress’ special Benghazi committee is being hyped as the biggest moment in the panel’s controversial existence. But the committee’s Republican leaders said Sunday they are equally, in not more, focused on new evidence and continued pursuit of the facts behind the fatal 2012 attacks. ...
